name: UNiagaraParameterDefinitions
doc: Collection of UNiagaraScriptVariables to synchronize between UNiagaraScripts.

bPromoteToTopInAddMenus: If true then these parameters will appear as top level entry in add menus (e.g. in the module editor)
MenuSortOrder: Defines the sort order in add menus. Entries with smaller numbers are displayed first.
